The '''Donkuwah knife''' was a type of primitive weapon used by the [[Donkuwah]] people during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

{{Weapon-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The Donkuwah knife and the [[Blackbane nail]] are represented by identical 3-D models.

